        public Vertice(T t,
               long poids,
               boolean sens)
        Constructor without the ending points of the vertex. The ending points are set to null.
        Parameters:
        t - The generic data
        poids - The vertex weight
        sens - Has this vertex a direction (true: first point to second, false: bidirectionnal)

      • Vertice

        Constructor with the ending points of the vertex. The ending points are set to null.
        Parameters:
        t - The generic data
        poids - The vertex weight
        ends - The list of two nodes composing the ends of the vertex
        sens - Has this vertex a direction (true: first point to second, false: bidirectionnal)
